        },
        {
          "text": "The classrooms are fully air conditioned and fully ventilated.",
          "name": "Raunak singh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "There's a ground available for students who are interested in sports. And it is quite good lot of sports availability. Facility are available in naval campus.",
